name: Fae Transfusion
description:
Transfer the life force of up to 4 enemies in the targeted area, dealing 39,065 Nature damage evenly split to each enemy target over 2.7 sec. 

Pressing Fae Transfusion again within 20 sec will release 60% of all damage from Fae Transfusion, healing up to 4 allies within 20 yds.
